    "verdict": "DISPROVEN",
    "reasoning": "The hypothesis is that the I-CSCF cannot communicate with the HSS. Probes revealed that the network path between the I-CSCF and the HSS is perfectly healthy, with near-zero RTT and no packet loss. A triangulation probe from the S-CSCF confirmed the HSS is reachable. This directly contradicts the hypothesis's claim of a communication failure. The issue is not at the network layer between I-CSCF and HSS.",
